      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for someone prioritizing mechanical functionality over aesthetics. The exterior shows visible signs of age, including several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining from regular use. While it has been regularly serviced and runs reliably, a prospective buyer should expect to address some minor interior trim issues and cosmetic imperfections to bring it back to its best.",
