    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really great shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014I\u2019ve always made sure to stay on top of oil changes and keep the interior nice and tidy. It runs like a dream and is just waiting for someone new to take it on some adventures. It's a solid, dependable car that still looks sharp in the driveway. Come by and take it for a test drive, I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
