    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-spec E46 M3 powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a glorious 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the factory variable M differential lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings, ensuring the chassis handles with the precision expected of an M-division product. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the powertrain remains robust with linear power delivery and a crisp exhaust note. A mechanically sorted icon for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Well-maintained vehicle. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Engine runs strong. Service records available.",
      "price": 31500.0,
