    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next road trip? I\u2019m parting ways with this beauty, and it\u2019s honestly such a joy to drive! It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, so it\u2019s in great shape and runs like a dream. It\u2019s perfect for anyone who wants a solid, high-quality vehicle without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
