    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power unit. This high-revving engine remains internally robust, benefiting from a recent comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and a valve clearance adjustment. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to the rear wheels via a functional M-Variable differential lock. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. Suspension components feature refreshed bushings, maintaining the sharp turn-in and communicative feedback characteristic of this platform. While the exterior displays minor stone chips and age-appropriate patina, the drivetrain exhibits exceptional health with no fluid leaks or timing chain noise. This is a driver-focused example optimized for performance and longevity.",
